name: QTZ - Tunnel #1
description: Quartz Composer was a visual programming language, it was my tool for making and performing live visuals for many years, because it allowed me to patch live and its performance was very good. At some point in 2014 I started using it to create loops and upload them as gif to tumblr. * The tricky part of the process was looping things without timeline, tunnels are ideal for that.
